msgstr "Die Geschichte von BibleTime"

#. Tag: para
#: software_about.xml:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back in June of 1999 Thomas Hagedorn, Thorsten Uhlmann and Joachim Ansorg started to work on a Bible study application for KDE 1.0."
